snippet.title: Detained: Too Good for School - Kickstarter Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam ▶️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394650/Detained_Too_Good_for_School
Kickstarter Pre-Launch Page ▶️ https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/otkgames/detained-too-good-for-school
Join O.T.K. Games Discord  ▶️ https://discord.gg/5JErJQ6vUx

You play as a school girl who doesn't obey the rules. Explore the open world, pick a fight with street mobs, work part-time in a club and then spend all your money in a jiffy, and enjoy a hot date. Your choices will eventually shape the future of the city.
